The patch stack in patches/ (0001, 0002) is applied to the PPSSPP source tree by
build.sh and modifies PPSSPP's own files (0001 adds `savestate.save`/
`savestate.load` and `emucap.screenshot` WebSocket debugger commands; 0002 fixes
headless exec breakpoints and single-step advance). It is therefore a
derivative work of PPSSPP (GPL-2.0-or-later) and is licensed GPL-2.0-or-later.
emucap does not ship PPSSPP's binary or source — build.sh clones and builds a
pinned upstream commit on your machine. See ../../NOTICE.

